# Buck-Boost Converter

This project focuses on the design and analysis of a DC-DC Buck-Boost Converter used for both step-up and step-down voltage conversion.

## Key Concepts:
- Voltage step-up and step-down operation
- Switching using MOSFET
- Output voltage polarity and regulation

## Tools Used:
- Basic calculations
- MATLAB/Simulink (if used)

## Applications:
- Electric vehicle power systems
- Battery voltage regulation
